[SN]TITLE[SN]
The Moroccan warrior women beating men at their own games

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
For centuries the Berber men of North Africa have proved their worth in the high octane, dangerous sport of Fantasia.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 June 2016 Last updated at 00:03 BST
Teams of riders charge together, firing their riles in unison.
But now for the first time, women have been taking them on... and winning!
Sahar Zand travelled to Morocco to meet the girls of Fantasia.
